---
description: Compiler Python — binary contracts, little-endian, file size checks
globs: compiler/**/*.py
alwaysApply: false
---

- All binary writes use '<f8' explicit little-endian float64
- Validate file size after every write: Path(p).stat().st_size
- model_weights.bin must be exactly 2060 bytes
- degree2_weights.bin must be exactly 4108 bytes
- Always save feature_idx.npy with dtype int64
